Names:
	red1
	green1
	blue1
	red2
	green2
	blue2


Info:
	newline(\n )for end line

Function:
	delay
		followed by space then number in milisecond
		could be done using time.sleep
	restart
		restart the code loop

Operation:

	{name}{operation sign}{number}
		operation signs:
			+,-,*,/
	{name} = {number}

